6:
Hey out there! Is everyone ready for
a show?!
10:
When Diva Media's on the air, all
your electrons stop and stare!
14:
We have a VERY special show for
you todayâ€”our line-up is off the
charts! Complete with a TON of
surprise guests!
23:
C'mon, now! We need you all to get
fired up! 'Cause this is gonna be one
hell of a blast!
27:
Ahahaha... Ohhh yeahhh. We're
bringing the boom...
31:
Wow... Holograms are great and all,
but fireworks sure hit differently
when they're the real deal.
35:
Who would have thought that
something as simple as gunpowder
would be capable of leaving such
an unforgettable impression?
43:
We have the best fans in the
universeâ€”I'll never forget the sound
of your cheers!
47:
So no matter what happens, I want
you all to remember this. Whether
you feel like laughing or crying...
you're not alone! I'll always be with
you in spirit!
52:
New directive confirmed: kicking it
into high gear!
58:
Here you are! I prepared some
special Shibuya-style sweet buns to
commemorate graduation day. Eat
up!
62:
Thanks! Mmm, these lookâ€”wait. Did
you use monster parts in these?
66:
Heh, not THIS time! I went more
traditional for the occasion. But I
have big news! I'll be opening a new
Monster Cuisine restaurant in
Palpebra!
74:
The investors said it'd be better for
business if I had some non-monster
dishes on the menu, too... Interested
in becoming my sous chef, Alk?
83:
I knew you'd say yes. Ever thought
about going pro?
87:
...I have, actually. I've been thinking
about starting up my own curry
house.
93:
Still stewing over the idea, I see. If
you're feeling unsure, you already
know what to do...
100:
Hmm. You've got me there, but... I
still need some time to think about it.
104:
Hehe! Take all the time you need. For
a chef, prep is everything! But that's
all for another day. Today, you
should focus on having FUN!
112:
WAAAHAHAHA! And now, the
moment you've all been waiting for...
Feast your eyes on my wondrous
work!
116:
Thanks to your contributions, my
masterpiece is complete! Bask in
the glory of my creation, the shining
beacon of graduation... The one, the
only... Tharros Ultimate!
128:
Just kidding! I bet you thought my
creation was about to pulverize you
all, eh? Well, that ain't happening!
Got you good, huh?
131:
Somebody HELP! That golem is
going to smash us all to bits!
135:
Yeah, see? It's gonna smash you all
toâ€”wait, what? No! STOP!
143: I knew it! It's gone haywire, yet again!
147:
Perhaps this golem running amok is
a manifestation of all of our
expectations... Almost like we willed
this to happen.
153:
That's ridiculous! Such a strong
manifestation could never occur,
unless somehow our fears were
justifiedâ€”
158:
Drat! Who could have known the
elite combat protocols and
state-of-the-art weaponry I
installed could come back to bite
me like this?!
163:
This IS all your fault, Dedalia! You're
supposed to be running this show,
so DO something about it!
167:
Welcome, one and all, to the Guild's
surprise smackdown event. Whoop,
whoop! Golem Hunting Season
starts NOW!
171:
Oh, and we've got prizes, too! Even if
you're trash. You'll probably get
wrecked... but hey, you can still give
it a shot!
176: Hehe, let us at 'em! I wanna go first!
179:
We're adventurers! Our job is to
overcome any obstacle, make the
impossible possible, and laugh in
the face of danger! And that golem
is looking mighty dangerous.
190:
*sigh* This place would give me
grey hair if it wasn't white already...
Some things never change, huh?
199:
You've got that right... This is just like
old times.
203: Do you want to join in, Alk?
207:
Yeah... I'd really hate to sit this one
out.
216:
No, I couldn't... Not for something so
silly.
221:
Go ahead. I wouldn't have it any
other way.
230: Wait. I need to ask you one last thing.
233: What do you want to do, Alk?
237:
Well, the first thing I want to do is
kick some golem butt. After I'm done
with that, I want to go on another
adventure with you and all of our
friends.
243:
And once things settle down, I'm
going to become the best curry chef
this world has ever seen!
253:
...I swear, Alk. If you die on me out
there, I'll drag you back from hell
myself just so I can whip your ass
AGAIN! You hear me?!
258:
Loud and clear, buddy! I'll make it
back in one piece. I promise.
272:
Damn it, you hunk of junk! Tharros,
activate infinity mode!
276:
Congratulations, grads and all! Step
up and try your luck with my lovely
little Tharros here! BRING IT ON!
280:
Oh, come on Ayumu! You had us all
worried, and now you're just gonna
steal the limelight?! So unfair!
284:
Golem Hunting Season is now in full
swing! Entry number, uh... ten? Alk,
representing Starview Village!
